CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 9, 2011

[Cite as 05/09/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-2194.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2009-1534. Mahoning Cty. Bar Assn. v. DiMartino.

It is ordered by this court, sua sponte, that Dennis A. DiMartino, Attorney Registration No. 0039270, last known business address in Youngstown, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of February 3, 2010, to wit: failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before March 5, 2010.
